title: INDOOR.3 | Happening Tonight!
body_text:
Diana, Edwards, Sascha, Valerie, Spenge, & Megill will be there. The Yochum, Londono, Brown, & Katz families? Confirmed!
Fitz + Stopa, Chris + Joanice, Steve + Stacey = They're In! My mom, step-dad, nephews, cousin, aunt, uncle, Anthony.. all attending!
It's been more than a year since the last ECD reunion.. what a wild and memorable night this will undoubtedly be!
